[Boing Boing blog](http://www.boingboing.net/2011/03/16/video-of-6-main-
japa.html) points us towards a video that shows us the programming in 6 main
TV channels in Japan during the Earthquake: sadly, most channels didn't even
bother to noticeably show the earthquake warning, opting instead for
continuing with the advertisements.
[TimeOutTokyo](http://twitter.com/#!/TimeOutTokyo/status/48174392781455360)
commented: “This is why we watch NHK.”

